Index to Names in A Flora of California
         
    This is a list of scientific names appearing in A Flora of California, Willis Jepson's never-completed magnum opus. It was produced nearly entirely by Tim Kask, a volunteer for the Jepson Library.

Images were made in collaboration with researchers at Xerox PARC and the Digital Library Project, UC Berkeley. The original high resolution TIF images have been converted to low resolution JPEG images to permit expeditious transfer and display.

Contact Richard Moe (rlmoe@berkeley.edu) about this page.

  

Clicking on a name will take you to the page in Jepson's Flora on which the name appears.
